Package: surveycto
Type: Package
Title: Manipulation of Data Collected through ODK-compliant Platforms
Version: 0.1.0
Author@R: c(
           person("Waiguru Muiruki", email="waigurusamuel@gmail.com"
Maintainer: The package maintainer <waigurusamuel@gmail.com>
Description: The package is used to manuplicate data collected through platform
             that use Open Data Kit(ODK) platforms such as SurveyCTO, kobo
             (either 'https://kobo.humanitarianresponse.info/' or
             'kc.kobotoolbox.org'), ODK central. The main purpose is to develop 
             live dashboard during data collection. There are functions to add
             value labels for both multiple and single variables from XLSFORM.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
